videos.description: Yves Pons cuts backdoor and rises up to catch and throw down alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Pons goes up high for an alley-oop

videos.description: Tennessee's Grant Williams posts up down low for a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Williams flushes home slam

videos.description: John Petty gets to the rim and converts the and-1 for Alabama.
videos.headline: Petty attacks the rim and converts and-1

videos.description: John Petty's scoop layup cuts Tennessee's lead to just one possession vs. Alabama.
videos.headline: Petty finishes nicely around the rim

videos.description: Grant Williams can't stuff the alley-oop down for a dunk but the ball still bounces into the basket anyways for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Williams gets bucket after failed alley-oop

videos.description: Donta Hall trails Alabama's fast break to throw down a putback jam.
videos.headline: Hall cleans up fast break with a huge putback slam

videos.description: Grant Williams stretches out to reject a potential go-ahead 3-pointer by Alabama late in the second half.
videos.headline: Williams makes a clutch block for Tennessee
